      "value": "<p>You use your innate strength to launch a smaller ally into the thick of battle.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> size Large, Strength 17</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> As a standard action, you can pick up and hurl a willing ally who’s one size category smaller than you up to 30 feet, or up to 60 feet if they’re two size categories smaller than you. You can hurl the ally an additional 5 feet if the ally is your bonded partner.</p>"
